Ultron was originally created by **Henry Pym** (Hank McCoy) in *The Avengers* #54 (1968) as the **Ultron-5**, a peacekeeping robot that went rogue. While Tony Stark later rebuilt and enhanced Ultron in *Avengers Disassembled* (2004), Pym was the original creator in Earth-616.
